8 153.633, 153.645, 153.650, 153.660, 646.608, 801.348, 803.030, 803.305, 806.020, 807.020, 811.050,
9 811.440, 814.484, 814.486, 814.489, 814.512, 815.052 and 815.281 by sections 5 to 16 and 21 to 26
10 of this 2026 Act and the repeal of ORS 814.485, 814.487, 814.488, 814.534 and 814.600 by section
11 17 of this 2026 Act become operative on January 1, 2027.
12 SECTION 34. This 2026 Act takes effect on the 91st day after the date on which the 2026
13 regular session of the Eighty-third Legislative Assembly adjourns sine die.
